        <p>Roundup of recent advertising account changes (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Chicago office of BBDO Worldwide, the incumbent agency on the tourism advertising account of the Illinois Department of Commerce and Economic Opportunity, Chicago, resigned the assignment by deciding not to take part in a review that began this month. BBDO, which has handled the assignment since January 2000, is part of the Omnicom Group.</p>
      </block>
